messages.content: Hello Mr. Satish. I apologise for not calling you at 11. Do let me know a time to schedule our call. Thank you for your understanding.
Please let me know if we can get on a call to discuss more about the investment opportunity
Yes we have an investment opportunity
So, is there something we can do wrt to land?
Hi, thanks for reaching out. We only deal in land.

Hello Team 1acre. I hope this message finds you well.

I am reaching out to you with an exciting proposition for collaboration.

At Alt DRX, we currently have compelling investment opportunities (FRACTIONAL INVESTMENT IN REAL ESTATE) available on our platform that we are eager to promote. We are confident that your expertise and reach in the industry would greatly enhance the visibility of these opportunities.

I would love to discuss this collaboration further at your earliest convenience. Please let me know a time that suits you to schedule a call or meeting.

Thank you for considering this proposal, and I look forward to the possibility of working together.

Best Regards,
Rajesh Chand
Sr. Manager - Investments
9916465658
www.AltDRX.com
